data.description: Fantastic ranch home with over 2100 square feet of finish.  This 2020 built home has great features including beautiful LVP flooring in the hallway, kitchen, dinette, and great room with fireplace. Gorgeous kitchen with white cabinetry, center island, quartz counters, stainless steel appliances including a brand new smooth top GE range (Sept. '23), pantry, dinette with sliders to an east-facing covered deck (perfect for shade in the evening) overlooking a large rear yard with a 6' wood privacy fence!  The large primary suite features a tiled shower, double sinks, and a walk-in closet. HUGE mudroom/laundry room. Two additional bedrooms, a full hallway bath, and a linen closet complete the main level. An attractive open stairwell leads to the finished walk-out lower level that boasts a very spacious family room, 4th bedroom, full bath, and large storage room w/potential for additional living space. BONUS: Solar panels save you an $'s on your electric bill.  The 24-month average for gas and electricity is a low $86.  EV ready as well with a 50 Amp plug installed in the garage. New Abbie Grove Elementary School under construction across the street will open in the Fall of 2024. All appliances including washer and dryer stay.  Other amenities:  neutral decor,  2' white blinds, brand new epoxy floor in the garage, and patio.
